node.text:
A day in the life of @hannah_voiro a Carlo’s Bakery Cake Designer. 🎂 
.
She’s creating one of our #oreo cakes here for you today! Check out that ganache drip 👌😋 
.
[featuring our Marlton, NJ Bakery]
.
Follow us over on @tiktok for more fun videos like this one. LINK IN STORIES
.
#carlosbakery #cakeboss #oreocake #ganache #ganachedrip #cake #caketutorial #oreo #tutorial #howto #cakemaking #cakevideo

node.text:
Our Individual Cheesecake Sampler comes in 4 incredible flavors for you to dress up!!!
.
-Traditional
-Strawberry
-Cookies & Cream
-Salted Caramel
.
⭐️Our classic cheesecakes have a silky texture and a rich, sweet flavor that pairs well with 
fresh fruit or a drizzle of warm chocolate. 
.
🤩Add an additional Individual Cheesecake Sampler for just $19.95!!!
.
👉Order at CarlosBakery.Goldbelly.com for FAST & FREE shipping anywhere in the U.S.
.
.
